e)\n   - Pharmaceutical and medical device random placement system\n   - Ranking system\n   - Medical device (vial, syringe, IV, etc.) sticker replacement system (brand, capacity, language)\n   - Multilingual system (Korean, English, Bednam)\n ", "short_description": "AcroXeR NursingVR education simulator optimized for the nursing medical environment that can enhance practical experience in various cases for hospitals lacking nursing staff dedicated to education."}]}, "developer_name": "Surgical Mind.Inc", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://acroxer.com/bbs/content.php?co_id=privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://acroxer.com/bbs/content.php?co_id=provision", "publisher_name": "unity", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://nursingvr.acroxer.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "514087707868786"}, {"id": "478089301798119"}, {"id": "1043107547362485"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "ko", "vi", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7736743289691495"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "434886815729270"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "434886815729270"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1720179133, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "434886815729270"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "9352592591439882", "version": "0.9.11"}, "id": "410251458276712", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7736743283024829", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9352592591439882"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1735627568, "id": "9361013657264442", "version": "0.9.11", "version_code": 34, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7736743283024829", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9352592591439882"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "410251458276712"}]}, "change_log": "- NursingVR <V 0.9.11>\n    - \uc8fc\uc694 \uc5c5\ub370\uc774\ud2b8\n        - \uae30\ub2a5 \ucd94\uac00 \ubc0f \uac1c\uc120\n            - \uc635\uc158 \uacc4\uc815 \uc5f0\ub3d9\n            - \ub85c\uadf8\uc778UI\n                - \uc544\uc774\ub514 \uc800\uc7a5\ud558\uae30 \ud1a0\uae00\ubc84\ud2bc \ucd94\uac00 : \ud1a0\uae00 \ud574\uc81c\ud558\uba74 \uc800\uc7a5\uc544\uc774\ub514\ub97c \uacf5\ubc31\ubb38\uc790\ub85c \uc800\uc7a5\n                - \ud328\uc2a4\uc6cc\ub4dc \uc800\uc7a5\ud558\uae30 \ud1a0\uae00\ubc84\ud2bc \ucd94\uac00 : \uc544\uc774\ub514 \uc800\uc7a5\uc2dc\uc5d0\ub9cc \uc720\ud6a8\n                - \ub85c\uadf8\uc544\uc6c3 \ubc84\ud2bc\uc744 UserID \uc544\ub798\uc5d0 \ucd94\uac00\n                - \ub85c\uadf8\uc544\uc6c3\ud558\uc2dc\uaca0\uc2b5\ub2c8\uae4c? \ud655\uc778 \ud31d\uc5c5 \ucd94\uac00\n                - \uc544\uc774\ub514/\ud328\uc2a4\uc6cc\ub4dc\ucc3d \ud0a4\ubcf4\ub4dc \ud65c\uc131\ud654\uc2dc \ud574\ub2f9 \ucc3d \ud14c\ub450\ub9ac \ucd9c\ub825\n              \n        - \ubc84\uadf8 \uc218\uc815\n            - \uc0c8 \uae30\uae30\ub85c \uccab \uc124\uce58\uc2dc \uacc4\uc815\uc815\ubcf4\uac00 \ub0a8\uc544\uc788\ub294 \ubb38\uc81c\n            - \uc2dc\ub098\ub9ac\uc624\n                - \uc790\uae30 \uc21c\uc11c\uac00 \uc544\ub2d0 \ub54c \uc218\uc561\ubc31\uc758 \uc218\uc561\uc138\ud2b8 \uc5f0\uacb0 \ub9c8\uac1c \uc5f4\uc5c8\uc744 \ub54c \uc815\uc0c1\uc801\uc73c\ub85c \uc9c4\ud589\ub418\uc9c0 \uc54a\ub294 \ubb38\uc81c\n                - \ud22c\uc57d\uc900\ube44\uc2e4\uc5d0\uc11c \uc778\ubca4\ud1a0\ub9ac\uc5d0 \ub69c\uaed1\ub123\uae30\uc804 \ud39c\uc744 \ub123\uc5c8\uc744 \ub54c \uc815\uc0c1\uc801\uc73c\ub85c \uc9c4\ud589\ub418\uc9c0 \uc54a\ub294 \ubb38\uc81c\n                - \ubc14\ub2e5\uc5d0 \ub5a8\uc5b4\uc9c0\uc9c0 \uc54a\uc558\ub294\ub370 \uacbd\uace0 \uba58\ud2b8\uac00 \ub098\uc624\ub294 \ubb38\uc81c\n                    - \uc18c\ub3c5\ud544\uc694\ud560 \ub54c [\ubc14\ub2e5\uc5d0 \ub5a8\uc5b4\uc9c4 \uac1c\ubd09 \ubc14\uc774\uc54c\uc740 \uc785\uad6c \uc18c\ub3c5\uc774 \ud544\uc694\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4.]  \uacbd\uace0 \uba58\ud2b8\uac00 \ub098\uc624\ub294 \uacbd\uc6b0 \uccb4\ud06c\n                - \uace0\uc8fc\uc758 \ud39c\ud615 \ud39c\ub2c8\ub4e4 \uacb0\ud569\uc2dc \ub9c8\uac1c\uc18c\ub3c5 \uc548\ud558\uba74 \uc815\uc0c1\uc801\uc73c\ub85c \uc9c4\ud589\ub418\uc9c0 \uc54a\ub294 \ubb38\uc81c\n                - \uac04\ud5d0\uc801\uc73c\ub85c \uace0\uc8fc\uc758 \ud22c\uc57d \uc644\ub8cc \ud6c4 '\uc19c 5\ucd08\uac04 \ub204\ub974\uae30' \uc2e4\ud589 \uc548 \ub418\ub294 \ubb38\uc81c\n    \n   **NursingVR <V 0.9.11>**\n\n### Major Updates\n\n### **Features Added and Improved**\n\n- **Option Account Integration**\n- **Login UI Enhancements**:\n    - Added \"Remember ID\" toggle button: When toggled off, the saved ID is cleared.\n    - Added \"Save Password\" toggle button: Only valid when \"Remember ID\" is enabled.\n    - Added a Logout button below the User ID display.\n    - Added a confirmation popup for \"Are you sure you want to log out?\".\n    - Highlighted border on the ID/password fields when the keyboard is activated.\n\n### **Bug Fixes**\n\n- **Account Management**:\n    - Resolved an issue where account information remained after the first installation on a new device.\n- **Scenario Bugs**:\n    - Fixed an issue where the process did not progress properly if the infusion bag's set connector cap was opened out of turn.\n    - Fixed an issue in the medication preparation room where the process would not progress correctly if the pen was placed in the inventory before the cap.\n    - Fixed a bug where warning messages appeared even though items had not fallen to the floor.\n    - Checked scenarios where a warning message, \"[The opening of a vial dropped to the floor needs to be disinfected.],\" appeared unnecessarily.\n    - Resolved an issue where the process did not proceed if the pen needle cap was not disinfected during pen-type syringe assembly for high-dose medication.\n    - Addressed a bug where the \"Press with cotton for 5 seconds\" step intermittently failed to execute after completing a high-dose injection.", "created_date": 1735484617, "id": "9352592591439882", "version": "0.9.11", "version_code": 33, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7736743283024829", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9352592591439882"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1735276078, "id": "9340303666002108", "version": "0.9.11", "version_code": 32,